text: Gholamreza Sabet Imani (, born 6 April 2000) is an Iranian footballer who plays as a Midfielder who currently plays for Iranian club Pars Jonoubi Jam in the Persian Gulf Pro League. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian footballers Category:Pars Jonoubi Jam players Category:Association football midfielders
